{"word":"G3068 - λούω - loúō - loo'-o - Wash","slug":"G3068","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">λούω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>loúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>loo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Wash"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - louo&#x0304;</b> - <i>loo'-o</i><p/>A primary verb; to <i>bathe</i> (the <i>whole</i> person; whereas <a href=\"#/G3538\">G3538</a> means to wet a <i>part</i> only, and <a href=\"#/G4150\">G4150</a> to wash, cleanse <i>garments</i> exclusively): - wash."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3067\">G3067</a>, <a href=\"#/G628\">G628</a>"}]}